{"tid":1018397,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北韓變了】似足南韓風 北韓女團背心熱褲獻唱","createTime":"2019-02-12T08:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T08:51:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e36ff5ff146bf634b0e541ace6c258830a00938","tid":1018397,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190209/large/1549703333_11ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190209%2Flarge%2F1549703333_11ba.jpg&h=1f99a1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190209/large/1549703334_cef8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190209%2Flarge%2F1549703334_cef8.jpg&h=e5425cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁歌熱舞的女團不是南韓獨有，近日有「北韓少女時代」之稱的「牡丹峰樂團」的影片紅到日本，網民瘋傳她們身穿背心熱褲演唱歌頌祖國富強的歌曲《走向未來》，帖子題為「這是現今的『北韓音樂』&hellip;&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n片段攝於「牡丹峰樂團」在中國的一次表演，台上五位女歌手穿上紅色背心黑色熱褲，露出長腿又唱又跳，舞蹈編排與時興的南韓女團相似，同台後方是身穿軍裝以不同樂器伴奏的表演者。<br />\n<br />\n網民還提供日文版歌詞和「牡丹峰樂團」舊時身穿軍裝制服的演出片段作對比。<br />\n<br />\n有網民大讚表演者身穿軍服加手持樂器非常型格，有人坦言看影片時目光離不開團員的美腿，形容：「戀足癖是沒有國界之分的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190211/59240305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59240305&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuoDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=0495b571\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59240305&h=9f37e6e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190211/59240305</a>"},{"pid":"20ac9ab8fdfecd6aa2383e39d523b83e09c1032b","tid":1018397,"uid":211461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Red velvet 改變北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc53875d27943f72d89c13ce844de19086ab3b98","tid":1018397,"uid":52881,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"軍服彈Bass,好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e397cc6ab1192ba41a3c163130481466ab4dff7a","tid":1018397,"uid":224967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"軍佬的浪漫"},{"pid":"d30cf59b0d50ed16231d426eb6135899fd3ccdee","tid":1018397,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}